sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Personal Particular Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open personal particular page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Load authenticated user's student profile
    LW->>DB: Load latest class, institute, campus
    DB-->>LW: Student and related records
    LW-->>UI: Render personal details table

    User->>UI: Refresh page
    UI->>LW: New request
    LW->>DB: Re-fetch latest profile data
    DB-->>LW: Current records
    LW-->>UI: Re-render details
